domekit.cc incoming

reference geodesic dome generation algorithms:
http://www.antiprism.com/other/dome/index.html

usage:
domekit.html is our sample application, open that thang in a browser
domekit.js is our code
domekit.cc/generator/index.html is the domekit.cc dome generator

You will need Closure Script to build this project. There is a Ruby
and a Java version of the Closure Script tool.  Your choice.

Ruby:

    gem install closure
    rackup
    (browse to:) http://localhost:8080/

Java:

    (download:) https://github.com/dturnbull/closure-script/downloads
    java -jar closure.jar
    (browse to:) http://localhost:8080/

Thanks!!!
